General comments: 128 x ""0 egg"" nests are failed nests. Includes small colony to the south of A1; Chick count comments: empty nests calc from original pop size owing to old nests under refurbishment by non breeders (where these old nests were prev covered by snow / ice) and new empty nests prob arising due to increased non breeder activity in the colonies (where approx 90% of individuals seen were either failed or non breeding birds and partners). NB unusual to see so many partners attending occupied nests - seen at Gourlay also for at least a week prior to North Point count.
